This script will be able to upload directory recursive. Using swift api. 

Require:

php5-cli
php5-curl
swift:
	sudo add-apt-repository ppa:swift-core/release
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get -y install python-software-properties swift

You have to use this script only with params: 
	--dir=local_dir_to_upload
	--user=username
	--key=user_key
	--host=remote_cloud_server
	--rm-files=[false/true] rm local files after upload
	--container=remote_container_name
	-s      list remote conrainers
	-o      list objects in remote container (USE ONLY WITH --container param)

